ucted from the resonance\nproperties of the frequency vector $\\omega$, and proving that it is a\nquasiperiodic function (and not periodic) with respect to $\\ln\\varepsilon$. In\nthis way, we emphasize the strong dependence of the estimates for the splitting\non the arithmetic properties of the frequencies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 1 Jun 2019 22:48:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-28"}
